{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureSphere Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            color: #f0f0f0;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4d4d 0%, #cc0000 100%);\n            color: white;\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5em;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .services h2, .about h2, .contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #ff4d4d;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #cc0000;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #262626;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: #ff4d4d;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 50px;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n            text-align: left;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n        }\n\n        .about-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            max-width: 400px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: #262626;\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #444;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #f0f0f0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff4d4d 0%, #cc0000 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #111;\n            color: #aaa;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Artistic elements */\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50%;\n            left: -50%;\n            width: 200%;\n            height: 200%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 77, 77, 0) 70%);\n            animation: pulse 8s infinite linear;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }\n            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }\n        }\n\n        .service-item:nth-child(odd) {\n            border-left: 5px solid #ff4d4d;\n        }\n        .service-item:nth-child(even) {\n            border-right: 5px solid #ff4d4d;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>SecureSphere</h1>\n        <p>Your digital fortress in an evolving threat landscape. We provide cutting-edge cybersecurity solutions to protect your most valuable assets.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"container services\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Vulnerability Assessment</h3>\n            <p>Identifying and analyzing weaknesses in your systems before attackers do. Proactive measures for robust defense.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Threat Intelligence</h3>\n            <p>Staying ahead of emerging threats with real-time data and analysis. Informed security strategies.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Incident Response</h3>\n            <p>Rapid and effective handling of security breaches. Minimizing damage and restoring operations quickly.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Security Consulting</h3>\n            <p>Expert guidance to build and maintain a comprehensive cybersecurity posture tailored to your business needs.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container about\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <div class=\"about-content\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <p>At SecureSphere, we are a team of dedicated cybersecurity professionals passionate about safeguarding businesses from digital threats. With years of experience and a commitment to innovation, we offer a holistic approach to security, ensuring your data and operations remain protected. We believe in transparency, expertise, and building lasting partnerships with our clients.</p>\n            </div>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/cc0000/ffffff?text=SecureSphere\" alt=\"Cybersecurity Abstract Art\" class=\"about-image\">\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container contact\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <form class=\"contact-form\">\n            <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureSphere Cybersecurity. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}